                "H.UPMANN", @"H. Upmann is a Cuban brand of premium cigars established by banker Hermann Dietrich Upmann (who also founded the H.Upmann & Co. bank in the island). The brand is currently owned by British corporation Imperial Brands. Cigars are manufactured by Habanos S.A. –the state-owned tobacco company– in Cuba, and Altadis in La Romana, Dominican Republic.
